{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "87726e86-1c5d-443c-8cbe-208069229259",
		"name": "InspectPro API",
		"description": "## Testing Workflow\n\nRun requests in this order for a complete end-to-end test:\n\n### Setup\n\n1. Register User\n    \n2. Login (User)\n    \n3. Login (Admin)\n    \n\n### Profile Management\n\n1. Get Current Profile\n    \n2. Update Current Profile\n    \n3. List All Profiles\n    \n\n### Credentials & VP Promotion\n\n1. Submit Credential\n    \n2. Update Credential Status - Approve\n    \n3. Submit a second credential (change type in body)\n    \n4. Update Credential Status - Approve (second credential)\n    \n5. Get Current Profile → should show VERIFIED_PROFESSIONAL\n    \n\n### Company Profile & Switching\n\n1. Create Company Profile\n    \n2. Switch to Company Profile\n    \n3. Switch to Personal Profile\n    \n\n### Subscriptions\n\n1. Get Current Subscription\n    \n2. Check Feature Access - PDF\n    \n3. Check Feature Access - Inspection\n    \n4. Webhook - Upgrade to ENHANCED\n    \n5. Get Current Subscription → verify ENHANCED tier\n    \n6. Webhook - Upgrade to PROFESSIONAL\n    \n7. Get Current Subscription → verify ENHANCED tier\n    \n\n### Token Management\n\n1. Refresh Token\n    \n2. Trigger Credential Expiration Job",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "36779516"
	},
